      Gets listings by one neighbourhood name
      Parameters:
      neighbourhood - the name of neighbourhood
      paging - whether the request should be paginated or not, i.e "true" (default) or "false"
      page - the page number, starting from index 0
      size - the number of listings on one page, default is 10
